# Governance

## Decision Making
AGRICORP is founder-led. All strategic decisions, partnerships, and approvals 
are managed by the core team to ensure speed and accountability.

## Standards & Compliance
We operate to international agricultural and food safety standards. 
All operations in Sierra Leone and future countries will follow local regulations 
plus our internal SOPs for quality, safety, and sustainability.

## Partnerships
We engage with government agencies, NGOs, and private investors through 
formal MOUs and contracts. All partnerships are reviewed by the core team.

## Transparency
Financials, land documents, and operational reports are maintained in this repository 
and shared with verified investors and partners upon request.

